```html
<div class="description">
  <div class="desc-item">
    <span class="desc">打印机打字效果展示~~~</span>
    <span class="cursor">｜</span>
  </div>
  <div class="desc-item">
    <span class="desc">学习新思想，争做新青年！</span>
    <span class="cursor">｜</span>
  </div>
</div>
```

